Description_lang: Increases Lichborne duration by ${$s1/1000} sec and while active damage taken is reduced by $49039s8%.

description_blz.en_US: Increases Lichborne duration by 2 sec and while active damage taken is reduced by 15%.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta la duración de Exánime nato 2 s, y mientras dura, el daño recibido se reduce un 15%.

description_blz.en_GB: Increases Lichborne duration by 2 sec and while active damage taken is reduced by 15%.

description_blz.zh_TW: 巫妖之軀的持續時間延長2秒，並在作用期間內，受到的傷害降低15%。
